---
import { Picture } from 'astro:assets';
import img from '~/assets/tito_xd-cafe-manager-by-frankuwu.png';
import { SiteDescription, SiteTitle } from '~/config';
import MarkdownLayout from '~/layouts/MarkdownLayout.astro';
---

<MarkdownLayout
	title={SiteTitle}
	description={SiteDescription}
	hide={['title', 'comments']}
	currentNav="Home"
>
	<div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-4 xl:flex-row">
		<Picture class="lg:max-w-sm" src={img} formats={['avif', 'webp']} alt="Tito_XD original character coffee master ver. by artist Frankuwu" loading="eager" />
		<div>
			<h1>路上辛苦了<br />喝点什么？☕️</h1>
			<div class="space-y-3">
				<p>我是 Tito_XD、今日轮值的店长，也可以叫我头头👋</p>
				<p>又是新的一年，忙忙碌碌就这样开始了。</p>
				<p>总归还是生活碎碎念，如果我的寥寥几字也能让你驻足停看，那也不错，谢谢。</p>
				<p><a href="/posts/rewind-2025">2025 年的 REWIND 在这里</a>，<a href="/posts/onward-2026">2026 年的 ONWARD 在这里</a>。欢迎光临，请开心。</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</MarkdownLayout>